{"tid":1797421,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"美國通過《2020國防授權法案》 香港人勢必勝利","createTime":"2019-12-25T11:49:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-25T13:34:55.000Z","uid":286309,"like":53,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"cc17ed9ca5af9545f44fd42505f196a777bacda5","tid":1797421,"uid":286309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T11:49:09.000Z","msg":"快啲入嚟，香港人必須意識到2020一定要有雙普選自治<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><a href=\"https://lih.kg/1785953\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1785953</a></span><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">美國將會2020更高調插手香港</span></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">香港人要配合美國<br />\n逼中共面對2020死期</span></span></div><br />\n<br />\n點解美國會咁做? 如下<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">A.《2020年美國年度國防授權法案》 <br />\n <strong><span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>直接用國防支出支持五大訴求，將香港納入國防事務</strong></span></strong><br />\nB.《美國-香港政策法》<br />\n <strong><span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">容許</span>港元可以自由兌換美元＋香港獨立嘅關稅區</span></strong><br />\nC.《香港人權與民主法案》<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: green;\">表明香港2020前實行五大訴求，否則廢除《政策法》<br />\n</span></strong></div><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n假如2020無做到<span style=\"color: green;\">五大訴求</span>並且停止警暴<br />\n美國會實行《香港人權與民主法案》<br />\n去廢除 《美國-香港政策法》<br />\n即係<span style=\"color: red;\">美國唔準<strong><span style=\"color: green;\">港元自由兌換美元，聯繫匯率收皮</span></strong></span> <br />\n+<br />\n <span style=\"color: red;\">香港無得再引入所有<strong><span style=\"color: green;\">美國敏感技術</span></strong></span><br />\n＝<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n港元死亡<br />\n澳元死亡<br />\n人民幣死亡<br />\n香港死亡<br />\n澳門死亡<br />\n大灣區死亡<br />\n中共死亡</span><br />\n<br />\n同時將會運用各種<strong><span style=\"color: green;\">國防手段去威逼中共</span></strong>，令五大訴求成功實行"},{"pid":"5daf87fa88e89b23ea5f402043bf13cf311ddf7b","tid":1797421,"uid":36065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T11:50:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ad3084aa57e672e8b7005e8467540779ee11ba5","tid":1797421,"uid":91511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T11:52:08.000Z","msg":"推 2020好關鍵"},{"pid":"153a1d10c1c993e11f348f278229d7968205e5bc","tid":1797421,"uid":90183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T11:52:35.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"8ade241e849abc96dc1d860b918a429bba36b8c8","tid":1797421,"uid":286309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T11:54:48.000Z","msg":"2020普選，唯一出路"},{"pid":"d7a3df6f2776097b64ac4dee62edb4236c0ec180","tid":1797421,"uid":286309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T11:54:58.000Z","msg":"2020普選，唯一出路"},{"pid":"7eb7e70c88a9ea449625ea778bceb5e4b0efb664","tid":1797421,"uid":286309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T11:55:09.000Z","msg":"2020普選，唯一出路"},{"pid":"cf5b3b7c271dbac4f3601ba14506c7436648a33d","tid":1797421,"uid":286309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T11:55:19.000Z","msg":"2020普選，唯一出路"},{"pid":"c683377f179442686781a609136a3572bd5a395b","tid":1797421,"uid":286309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T11:55:29.000Z","msg":"2020普選，唯一出路"},{"pid":"5f161a193ac27b26b3c3ab6fdb04fce68ce85fff","tid":1797421,"uid":141565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T11:56:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cdbdf0fef720c36079cefccf7f5ec2bb03f993e5","tid":1797421,"uid":158404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T11:57:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"44c75cc5e88346a37d323ced64cbf391ce615c50","tid":1797421,"uid":127575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T12: